@mybbcat You can use the `save` arguments to store the information and pass to the next process.

Refer to http://docs.pyspider.org/en/latest/apis/self.crawl/#save

example:

```python
class Handler(BaseHandler):
    ...
    @config(age= 60)
    def login_page(self, response):
        self.crawl(url='https://baidu.com', 
                   callback=self.list_page, 
                   save={'cookies': response.cookies})

    @config(age= 2 * 60 * 60)
    def list_page(self, response):
        cookies = response.save['cookies']
        print cookies
```

