@mlin Thanks for the stack trace. It looks like this connection reset is originating from PyOpenSSL rather than requests in this case. This appears to have tripped up a few other projects as well and is an open issue in urllib3 since 2014 as the consensus appears to be that urllib3 should normalize the error.

In a clean virtual env environment with just blobxfer and its dependencies (or using the docker image), the same error should not manifest itself. Can you confirm?

I will work on adding special handling for when requests/urllib3 uses PyOpenSSL.

